You can simply ask Alexa to control your Indurama products. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1) Download our "Indurama Living" app in Google Play or iOS App Store, then register an account;
(2) Configure our devices in "Indurama Living" app and change appropriate name for your devices;
(3) Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android, ios or Amazon app market then configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(4) Search "Indurama Living" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(5) Enable "Indurama Living" skill, and you'll be navigated to "Indurama Living" login page;
(6) Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(7) Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
"Alexa, turn on clean robot"
"Alexa, turn off clean robot"
"Alexa, set the oven to turn off in 30 minutes"
